# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# tesboard — BUILD-TIME client env (read by Vite, baked into the browser
# bundle). Copy to `.env`.
#
# This file holds ONLY the VITE_* vars. Everything else is server-only:
#   • Local dev  → .dev.vars        (see .dev.vars.example)
#   • Production → wrangler.jsonc `vars` (non-secret) + `wrangler secret put`
#
# Rule: never VITE_-prefix a secret — anything with VITE_ ships to the browser.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Browser-side Supabase (dashboard login via Supabase Auth). The anon key is
# RLS-gated and safe to ship to the client.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
